section.para:
The Tracker project was undertaken to provide;




			Livestock information technology analysts, designers, and developers 
			a framework for the creation of software solutions useful for livestock producers and
			infrastructure providers;





			Low cost development solution to enable both large and
			small scale deployment of Livestock Information Technology application solutions;





			A common industry development environment for the creation of a livestock event history
			inter-exchange solutions.

			Software Application Products built from the Tracker Livestock Information
			Framework are used by livestock producers, infrastructure providers
			and process control auditors as effective, low cost solutions for;



recording animal event history;



maintaining production efficiency;



improving product quality;



documenting process control.
